The usual readiness probes and liveness probes.

If the wm is not ready it will be removed by the ep of a svc so it does not receice traffic. 

The liveness is the same but when the vm is already running and it fails it gets removed from the ep behing the svc.

THe usual properties: 
- initialDelaySeconds;
- periodSeconds;
- timeoutSeconds; 
- failureThreshold;
- successThreshold. 


The probes you can do are: httpGet o exec.

